{"tid":2300550,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"警暴終有結論！（李柱銘）","createTime":"2020-11-25T15:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T15:22:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"52a583f01150d576d3005d1f8ac3fbc20bd7da41","tid":2300550,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/MSMDTEGVVJHD3POAWD7WG3GLMM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FMSMDTEGVVJHD3POAWD7WG3GLMM%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=6b3d0492\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FMSMDTEGVVJHD3POAWD7WG3GLMM%2F&h=402df749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/MSMDTEGVVJHD3POAWD7WG3GLMM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警暴終有結論！（李柱銘）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DRyefAbGR81Yt-ZwQGZ5iVb_3aA=/1111x700/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ACBU45AZANDNVMH5KENCJAKOD4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDRyefAbGR81Yt-ZwQGZ5iVb_3aA%3D%2F1111x700%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FACBU45AZANDNVMH5KENCJAKOD4.gif&h=c4a16699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩層投訴機制均無效<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府曾聘請國際警政專家參與監警會的調查，但他們於去年底集體請辭，指監警會缺乏獨立調查能力。當中的專家之一、英國基爾大學心理學教授Clifford Stott，在上周聯同幾位專家、學者在學術網站發表論文，指出警方在去年6月12日針對包圍立法會的執法行動，無差別地使用過度武力，對付反送中運動的和平示威者，正是導致運動激進化的源頭。不過，保安局卻不予置評，顯然，政府根本無法反駁此報告提出的論述。<br />\n<br />\n由此歸納起來，現行調查警察投訴的兩層機制都無效，以及在政府縱容下，警暴肆虐和選擇性執法，導致市民的示威激進化，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李柱銘"},{"pid":"cdbdc5ac5e7f51d6c446547e39005e2f99ba41a0","tid":2300550,"uid":99725,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:17:04.000Z","msg":"死廢老嗰頭近就收嗲準備身後事la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5951d7547b9bd2f67b9825dbf42e40e3e65d2b7f","tid":2300550,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"話時話正苦好似真係無回應過Clifford篇文"},{"pid":"059829e9dcf74416e8e75f9f261f13d5ec5c89ce","tid":2300550,"uid":16034,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T15:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗有報應就係人都想 不過由你老口中講出黎無咩說服力"}]}